## ğŸ“ File Structure

- `verahession/api.py` â€“ Vera API interface (LLM)
- `verahession/assistant.py` â€“ Local trainer & classifier tools
- `intents.json` â€“ Training data for intent classification
- `model.pth` â€“ Output model file after training

